#74 and going strong! 💪 

Just dropping a little inspiration from @richardtomlinson2 and his practice, to remind you to stay on it… or to get started! It will do great things for you. 

Richard also does strength training, and has a balanced way of eating, sleeping, and living, which goes hand in hand with a healthy yoga practice. 

I’ve been working with him for over 10 years now, and have watched him recover quickly from three different surgeries, only to continue to work on building a great quality of life. 

Happy 74, and to many more! 🤍

#yogapractice #ashtangayoga #healthyliving #longevity #breath #healthylifestyle

Exciting News: Introducing Vagal LLC! 💫

We're thrilled to introduce you to Vagal LLC, a labor of love years in the making. We're on a mission to empower you, your families, and your businesses with the newest, simplified, hands-on experience knowledge to optimize your health and lead better lives. 🌿🧘‍♀️

🧠 What is Vagal? The vagal nerve, also known as the vagus nerve, is a crucial cranial nerve that regulates heart rate, digestion, and promotes relaxation, restoration, and recovery. It's the key to holistic well-being. 

👥 Meet the Minds Behind Vagal:

Alexia Bauer, Founder/Presenter: A transformational journey from Architecture to Yoga. With 15 years of experience, she's here to guide your physical and mental transformation.

Robert Dannenberg, Program Creator/Presenter: From boxing to holistic health, Robbie's decade-long journey brings a unique perspective to Vagal.

💼 Vagal's Offerings:
🌱 Personal Consultations
🏢 Corporate Seminars
📚 Wellness Pathways Seminars
🌄 Weekend Retreats

Join us on this transformative journey to a healthier, more fulfilling life with Vagal. Follow us for updates and valuable insights! 📆🌟 @vagal.io 

Thank you for supporting our mission. Together, we'll achieve optimum health and wellness! 💪

📅 Save the Date: Our next Wellness Pathways Seminar: - "Bio-Boost Holidays: How to Thrive During the Social Season" is on Saturday, November 18, 2023, from 11:00 AM to 1:30 PM. Don't miss it! 📌🗓️

#VagalLLC #WellnessJourney #HealthAndWellness #EmpowerYourHealth

Explore the stunning Adriatic coast in between grounding asanas, soothing pranayama, and reflective yogic practices as A+B bring ancient yogic wisdom to life to help you uncovering your true self.

Most days I practice by myself, and even though I enjoy how quiet it is, I LOVE to practice in a room full of students in a led primary series setting. The heat in the room from everyone moving a the pace of the Sanskrit counts is hard to compare to any other type of practice. ✨

Join me, @sleek.chameleon and @bpiacenti on Wednesdays at @yogaview at 6pm for a led half primary series until 2/21/24. ⚡️💫

#ashtangayoga #ledprimaryseries #yogapractice
